<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Petrovac, 23 Apr (TANJUG) -- Throughout the day and 
at various time intervals, particularly this afternoon, NATO 
planes have been violating the air space over Petrovac, Drvar, 
Kljuc, the Serb municipality of Bihac, Krupa on the Una River, 
and other municipalities in the western part of the republic of 
Srpska. Supersonic aircraft carried out low-altitude and 
