<H3> <TI>   Deliveries to Plants To Continue </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deliveries to Plants To Continue </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2604115294 Warsaw PAP in English 1118 GMT 26 Apr 94--FOR 
