  [Text] Tirana, April 22 (ATA) -- A delegation from the 
Great Britain, made up of representatives of the Foreign Office, 
the Major cabinet, and the British Embassy in Belgrade was not 
allowed by Belgrade authorities to visit Kosova, says a report 
